@10390    = ~This robe has been specially enchanted to meet the eclectic needs of the adventuring wizard. Aside from protecting the wearer from various forms of bludgeoning damage and mind-affecting spells, it also allows the wearer to protect their adventuring party from their own fireballs.

STATISTICS:

