Level: Clr 1, Drd 1, Rgr 1
Range: Caster
Duration: 30 rounds or until used up
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

This spell enhances the caster's sling bullets. Any bullet the caster throws will deal an additional 1d4+1 damage, and nonmagical bullets will be treated as +1 weapons. The spell ends once the caster has thrown a certain number of bullets: five plus one per caster level (maximum of 15 at level 10).

Although rangers normally cast spells at half their caster level, Magic Stone will be cast at a ranger's full caster level.~
@32107     = ~Protection from Evil
(Abjuration) [Good]
Level: Clr 1, Pal 1, Sor/Wiz 1
Range: Touch
Duration: 10 rounds / level
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: None

This spell forms a magic barrier around the target creature, giving evil creatures a -2 penalty to hit them, and reducing the save DC of spells and abilities from evil creatures that would hit them by 2. In additions, the creature is immune to charm and domination effects. Summoned fiends will not attack their summoner or their summoner's allies if their summoner has Protection from Evil.~
